{"tid":1718083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［緊急］中大而加面對一個好嚴峻既問題 直接影響成敗關鍵","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T23:46:36.000Z","uid":302038,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"333c927826c53a7dc46ed89e2bc920527c30f0fb","tid":1718083,"uid":302038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:22:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾清唔走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n首先好多謝大家送物資入中大 今日見好多人踩單車去幫手送大量物資入去 又有人鏈傳物資上山 大家咁團結真係好令人感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係問題尼啦 而加班死popo封撚曬好多出入口同路段 而且好多工友又無得番工 變相啲垃圾積少成多 長遠尼講係一何好大既問題 啲popo分分鐘咩都唔做 等啲垃圾堆爆中大已經贏硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好彩 而加只係積左兩日 仲有所以希望 只要大家一齊諗諗計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲個問題好快可以解決 大家幫幫拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c120c847997ab2e78e39910a70ca66add48791","tid":1718083,"uid":302038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:03.000Z","msg":"自推10連開始 1/10"},{"pid":"2873885120f4a477f13644616288f50eefa6e5f1","tid":1718083,"uid":302038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"